CHANGELOG
This file lists all the updates made to our Multi-tool Study Assistant App.

Version v1.0.0 – July 15, 2025
First version of the app
User can:

* Use a basic calculator (add, subtract, multiply, divide)

Version v1.0.1 – August 2, 2025
Second version of the app
User can:

* Use a basic calculator
* Convert units (length, weight, capacity)

Version v1.0.2 – September 5, 2025
Update version
User can:

* Use a basic calculator
* Convert units with cleaner rounded results

Version v1.1.0 – October 10, 2025
Major update
User can:

* Use a basic calculator
* Convert units
* Set up a timer for study

Version v1.1.1 – November 3, 2025
Update version
User can:

